    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for everyday transportation. The engine and transmission are in good working order, ensuring a reliable drive, though the car does show some visible wear and tear both inside and out. It has been maintained to ensure mechanical soundness, making it a solid option for anyone seeking functionality over cosmetic perfection. Buyers can expect a trustworthy vehicle that is ready for the road.",
